SubjectComposition of the Treasury Board
PrecisOrder (1) terminating the nominations made by Order in Council P.C. 2015-6 of January 5, 2015; and (2) nominating the Members of the Queen's Privy Council who shall constitute the TREASURY BOARD, and the alternates who may serve in their place.
